data.text:
Welcome to Dhamdhama Anchalik College

Dhamdhama Anchalik College establish in the year 1988 at the initiative of the enthusiastic people of the locality was a long cherished dream of the of this remote area. Dhamdhama Anchalik College has successfully completed 25 years of its glorious existence. Since its inception, the institution is imparting higher education to the economically backward classes of this locality, especially belonging to SC and ST communities. The college has greatly contributed to the academic and cultural atmosphere of the locality by its consistent effort and performance. The untiring effort of the dedicated teachers and the Management has turned the college into leading institution of Nalbari District.
